* 登上愛民頓愛斯基摩人足球隊榮譽牆（1983年<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.esks.com/page/history-woh|title=Edmonton Eskimos - Wall of Honour|accessdate=2011-09-21|publisher=愛民頓愛斯基摩人足球隊|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101028173300/http://esks.com/page/history-woh|archivedate=2010-10-28}}</ref>）
